---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="About"
  description="Christine Cheong is a Data Science Lecturer with experience teaching across university and executive education settings. Learn her story and approach."
>

  <!-- ── Page header ─────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="eyebrow anim anim-1">About</p>
      <h1 class="page-header__h1 anim anim-2">Christine Cheong</h1>
      <p class="page-header__sub anim anim-3">Data Science Educator &mdash; NUS-ISS</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="hr" />

  <!-- ── Main content ────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="about-layout wrap">

      <!-- Story -->
      <div class="prose">
        <p class="prose__lead">
          I&rsquo;m a data science lecturer with experience teaching in both university and
          executive education settings. My work sits at the intersection of rigorous academic
          grounding and practical, workplace-ready skills.
        </p>

        <p>
          I came to education through a career in data &mdash; and the thing that kept striking me
          was this: the hardest part of working with data is rarely the analysis itself. It&rsquo;s
          helping people understand what the data is actually saying, and why it matters. That
          realisation shapes how I teach. I know what it looks like when someone finally gets it,
          and I design my sessions to get people there faster.
        </p>

        <h2>What I believe about teaching data science</h2>

        <p>
          Most people don&rsquo;t struggle with data science because it&rsquo;s too hard.
          They struggle because it&rsquo;s taught poorly &mdash; with too much theory, too little
          context, and examples that bear no resemblance to the decisions they&rsquo;ll actually face.
        </p>

        <p>
          My approach is different. Every concept I teach is anchored to a real use case. Every
          exercise is designed to build genuine confidence, not just exam performance. I&rsquo;d
          rather a participant leave slightly slower but genuinely understanding than fast and fuzzy.
        </p>

        <h2>Background</h2>

        <ul class="prose__list">
          <li>Data Science Lecturer, NUS-ISS</li>
          <li>[Previous roles or industry experience &mdash; add yours here]</li>
          <li>[Relevant qualifications or credentials]</li>
          <li>[Specialisations &mdash; e.g. machine learning, applied statistics, Python]</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Beyond the classroom</h2>

        <p>
          [2&ndash;3 sentences on what you do outside of teaching &mdash; writing, research,
          consulting, speaking, or what keeps you connected to the field.]
        </p>

        <div class="prose__cta">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Get In Touch</a>
          <a href="/courses" class="btn btn--ghost">See My Courses</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Sidebar -->
      <aside class="about-sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <p class="sidebar-card__label">Teaching Areas</p>
          <ul class="sidebar-card__list">
            <li>Data Science Fundamentals</li>
            <li>Machine Learning</li>
            <li>Data Literacy for Leaders</li>
            <li>Applied Statistics</li>
            <li>Python for Data Analysis</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <p class="sidebar-card__label">I Work With</p>
          <ul class="sidebar-card__list">
            <li>University students</li>
            <li>Executive education participants</li>
            <li>Corporate training programmes</li>
            <li>Programme coordinators</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-card sidebar-card--accent">
          <p class="sidebar-card__label">Contact</p>
          <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-2);margin-bottom:var(--sp-4);">
            Open to questions, course enquiries, and speaking opportunities.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary" style="width:100%;justify-content:center;">
            Get In Touch
          </a>
        </div>
      </aside>

    </div>
  </section>

</Base>

<style>
  /* Page header */
  .page-header {
    padding: var(--sp-10) 0 var(--sp-8);
    background: var(--surface);
  }
  .page-header__h1 {
    font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 64px);
    margin-top: var(--sp-3);
    letter-spacing: -.02em;
  }
  .page-header__sub {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--text-2);
    margin-top: var(--sp-3);
  }

  /* Layout */
  .about-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
    gap: var(--sp-10);
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* Prose */
  .prose { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--sp-5); }
  .prose__lead {
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .prose p  { font-size: 17px; color: var(--text-2); line-height: 1.85; }
  .prose h2 {
    font-size: 28px;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-top: var(--sp-4);
    padding-top: var(--sp-5);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .prose__list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--sp-2);
    padding-left: var(--sp-4);
  }
  .prose__list li {
    list-style: disc;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-2);
  }
  .prose__cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--sp-3);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    padding-top: var(--sp-4);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-top: var(--sp-4);
  }

  /* Sidebar */
  .about-sidebar { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--sp-4); }
  .sidebar-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: var(--sp-5) var(--sp-6);
  }
  .sidebar-card--accent {
    background: var(--accent-light);
    border-color: #D0D9F5;
  }
  .sidebar-card__label {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: .1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-3);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-4);
  }
  .sidebar-card__list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--sp-2); }
  .sidebar-card__list li {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-2);
    padding: var(--sp-2) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .sidebar-card__list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .about-sidebar { order: -1; }
  }
</style>
